➜自吹自擂自陶醉
http://www.sohu.com/a/420508687_100281316	12789
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200924/d62193925897457e9ed7c90367d1c080.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 文化阴阳呈两面，对错全凭自说圆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 虚伪积习谁堪比，博大精深贻笑谈。 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200924/c63b4918554f4d9dab0bdb6c158f4c04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 冷眼世间假成真，废话蔽日是凡尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 自吹自擂自陶醉，自生自灭自沉沦.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200924/b5c32a7df96f4b2d8d129d614fab3f3d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鼓瑟无需识音律，南郭因何乱吹竽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人间万事仔细看，是非美丑搅迷离。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200924/c789b81e3d494ad6a6dc3441f5d6322c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>